name: Wonderful Life
description:
“Alone getting high on a Saturday night, I’m on the edge of a knife. Nobody cares if I’m dead or alive, oh what a wonderful life.” 

Inspired by the lyrics of Bring Me the Horizon - Wonderful Life

Get high and just keep balancing on a knife-edge;to be in a situation in which nobody knows what is going to happen next. No puff puff pass, all for you! ;)
